genresAdvancedInfo.name: nuevo tango
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre is a contemporary take on the traditional Argentine tango. It incorporates elements of jazz, classical music, and electronic music, and often features innovative instrumentation and arrangements. Nuevo tango is characterized by its complex rhythms and emotional intensity, and its lyrics often explore themes of love, loss, and nostalgia. This genre has gained a following among both tango purists and fans of experimental music.
